'''OpenSocial'''是一套为基于[[万维网|web]]的[[社交网络服务|社交网络服务]]提供的[[API|API]]。由[[Google|Google]]、[[MySpace|MySpace]]和其他一些社交网络服务共同开发。

OpenSocial于2007年11月1日发布。
<ref name="press release">{{cite web |url=http://www.google.com/intl/en/press/pressrel/opensocial.html |title=Google Launches OpenSocial to Spread Social Applications Across the Web |accessdate=2007-10-31 |date=2007-11-01 |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |doi= |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69Y7JuZmX?url=http://googlepress.blogspot.com/2007/11/google-launches-opensocial-to-spread_01.html |archivedate=2012-07-30 |quote= |dead-url=no }}</ref>
部署OpenSocial APIs的程序可以与任何支持这些API的系统[[互操作|互操作性]]，包括在[[Hi5.com|Hi5.com]]、[[MySpace|MySpace]]<ref name="MySpace">{{cite web |url=http://www.google.com/intl/en/press/pressrel/myspace_opensocial.html |title=MySpace and Google Join Forces to Launch Open Platform for Social Application Development |accessdate=2007-11-02 |date=2007-11-01 |publisher=[[Google|Google]] |doi= |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69Y7KN5RK?url=http://googlepress.blogspot.com/2007/11/myspace-and-google-join-forces-to_01.html |archivedate=2012-07-30 |quote= |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[orkut|orkut]]、[[Netlog|Netlog]]<ref name="Netlog.com">{{cite web|url=http://en.netlog.com/go/developer/opensocial|title=Developer / OpenSocial|accessdate=2008-09-17|publisher=[[Netlog|Netlog]]|doi=|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69Y7KoqYo?url=http://en.netlog.com/go/developer/documentation/article=opensocialapi|archivedate=2012-07-30|quote=|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、[[Sonico.com|Sonico.com]]<ref name="Sonico.com">{{cite web |url=http://blog.sonico.com/boletin/opensocial-week-exitoso-paso-por-argentina/ |title=OpenSocial Week: Exitoso paso por Argentina |accessdate=2008-06-05 |date=2008-05-05 |publisher=[[Sonico|Sonico]] |doi= |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69Y7Lad7f?url=http://blog.sonico.com/opensocial-week-exitoso-paso-por-argentina/ |archivedate=2012-07-30 |quote= |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[Friendster|Friendster]]<ref name="Bebo">{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/11/02/technology/02google.html |title=MySpace Joins Google Alliance to Counter Facebook |accessdate=2007-11-02 |last=Helft |first=Miguel |coauthors=Brad Stone |date=2007-11-02 |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |publisher=[[The_New_York_Times_Company|The New York Times Company]] |pages= |language= |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081211173736/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/11/02/technology/02google.html |archivedate=2008-12-11 |quote= |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[Ning|Ning]]和[[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]]网站上的功能。

== 结构 ==

{{Expand|section|date=2007年11月}}
OpenSocial基于[[HTML|HTML]]、[[JavaScript|JavaScript]]和[[Google_Gadgets|Google Gadgets]]框架，为社交应用提供4个API来读取数据和社交网络的核心功能。<ref name="Andreessen">{{cite web |url=http://blog.pmarca.com/2007/10/open-social-a-n.html |title=Open Social: a new universe of social applications all over the web |accessdate=2007-10-31 |last=Andreessen |first=Marc |authorlink=Marc Andreessen |date=2007-10-31 |work=blog.pmarca.com |publisher= |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071102041108/http://blog.pmarca.com/2007/10/open-social-a-n.html |archivedate=2007-11-02 |quote= |deadurl=yes }}</ref>每个API涉及一个方面：一个是通用的[[JavaScript|JavaScript]] API、一个是用于读取好友和关系信息的API、一个是用于发布和读取用户活动的API、和用於維持（這是給無伺服器狀態應用程式的簡單關鍵值配對資料）。<ref name="API documentation">{{cite web|url=http://code.google.com/apis/opensocial/docs/index.html|title=OpenSocial API Documentation|accessdate=2007-11-02|work=Google Code|publisher=Google|doi=|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69Y7M5S2I?url=https://developers.google.com/opensocial/|archivedate=2012-07-30|quote=|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

