=== 部署 ===

在OpenSocial发布时，[https://web.archive.org/web/20100417012201/http://code.google.com/apis/opensocial/partners.html 合作伙伴]承诺支持OpenSocial API，包括社交网络公司[[Bebo|Bebo]]、[http://engage.com Engage.com]{{Wayback|url=http://engage.com/ |date=20200614235313 }}、[[Friendster|Friendster]]、[[hi5_(website)|hi5]]、[[Hyves|Hyves]]、[[imeem|imeem]]、[https://web.archive.org/web/20181108181032/http://netmodular.com/  NetModular]、[[mixi|mixi]]、[[MySpace|MySpace]]、[[Ning|Ning]]、[[orkut|orkut]]、[[Plaxo|Plaxo]]、[[QuePasa|QuePasa]]、[[phpFox|phpFox]]、[[Six_Apart|Six Apart]]、[http://www.freebar.com Freebar.com]{{Wayback|url=http://www.freebar.com/ |date=20160605081227 }}；同时还包括商业导向网络公司[[LinkedIn|LinkedIn]]、[https://web.archive.org/web/20130929020812/http://www.tianji.com/ Tianji]、[[Salesforce.com|Salesforce.com]]、[http://viadeo.com Viadeo]{{Wayback|url=http://viadeo.com/ |date=20130209024008 }}、[[Oracle|Oracle]]和[[XING|XING]]。<ref name="press release" />[[Plaxo|Plaxo]]和[[Ning|Ning]]在OpenSocial发布当天就支持了OpenSocial，Plaxo对其Pulse功能加入了OpenSocial支持，<ref name="Plaxo Pulse">{{cite web |url=http://blog.plaxo.com/archives/2007/11/opensocial_is_n.html |title=OpenSocial is now live on Plaxo Pulse |accessdate=2007-11-04 |last=Smarr |first=Joseph |date=2007-11-01 |work=Plaxo's Personal Card |publisher=[[Plaxo|Plaxo]] |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080118124641/http://blog.plaxo.com/archives/2007/11/opensocial_is_n.html |archivedate=2008-01-18 |quote= |deadurl=yes }}</ref>而Ning加入了OpenSocial基本支持，早于其早前宣布的<ref name="Ning live">{{cite web |url=http://blog.ning.com/2007/11/andwere_live_with_opensocial_g.html |title=And ... We're Live with OpenSocial! |accessdate=2007-11-04 |last=Bianchini |first=Gina |date=2007-11-02 |work= |publisher=[[Ning|Ning]] |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071212234351/http://blog.ning.com/2007/11/andwere_live_with_opensocial_g.html |archivedate=2007-12-12 |quote= |deadurl=yes }}</ref>在2007年末到2008年初加入支持。<ref name="Ning plan">{{cite web |url=http://blog.ning.com/2007/